title: Ní Chuilín congratulates McKillop and Smyth on world gold medals (Northern Ireland Executive)
text: ( Source : Northern Ireland Executive ) Sports Minister Carál Ní Chuilín has congratulated Jason Smyth and Michael McKillop on winning gold medals at the IPC Athletics World Championships in Doha . ~ Saturday, 24 October 2015 Jason won the T13
